snippet.title: OCTOPATH TRAVELER II - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
OCTOPATH TRAVELER II is coming to Nintendo Switch on February 24, 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/octopath-traveler-ii-switch/

Eight new travelers journey through the land of Solistia, each with their own story to tell.

What will happen when their paths intertwine, and where will their adventures lead them … and you?

#OctopathTravelerII #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
